{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_09_01",
  "title": "成宮すず 1話 念願のCM",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "「――今年のバレンタインも、あなたと一緒に」……\nはぁぁ～……麻奈様は何度見ても麗しいですわ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"――This Valentine's Day‚ with you again\"…\nHaaa… Mana-sama is so beautiful no matter how many times I watch it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5866.666666599999,
          "startTime": 11.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すず、お疲れ様。ん？　それは……\n麻奈のバレンタインのCMか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu‚ good work. Hmm? Is that…\nMana's Valentine's Day CM?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.7999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "その通りですわ！　毎年この時期になると\n決まってこのCMを観返したくなるんですの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right! Every year around this time‚\nI always feel like looking back at this CM.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.466666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "俺も毎年、すずと同じように観返してるよ\n繰り返し観たくなるんだよな、麻奈のCMは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I also rewatch it every year‚ just like Suzu.\nMana's CMs always make me want to watch them over and over again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.6333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですのよ！　一度ならず二度、いえ……\n何度でも観たくなるのが麻奈様の魅力ですわよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Exactly! Not just once or twice‚ but…\nMana-sama's charm makes you want to watch them again and again!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.0704227667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "「私から君へのバレンタインチョコだよ\nもちろん本気の本気。本命チョコ」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"This is my Valentine's chocolate for you.\nOf course‚ it's truly my true feeling chocolate.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.566666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "「……照れないの。君は鈍いんだから\nこれくらいはっきり言わなきゃ伝わらないでしょ？」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"……Don't be shy. Since you're so dense‚\nI have to be this clear for you to understand‚ right?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.6312394869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "「ふふっ、もうこれで逃げられないよ？\n早く気持ちを聞かせて？」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Fufu‚ you can't run away now‚ can you?\nTell me how you feel?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.4159636609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "「……私のこと、どう思ってるの？」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"……How do you feel about me?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "残る台詞は……きゃーーーー！\nこ、これ以上はとても言えませんわ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The rest of the lines are… kyaaaaa!\nI-I can't say anymore~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.7766190172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いったん落ち着いてくれ……とはいえ、それだけ\nはっきり覚えてるのは凄いな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Calm down for a second… But still‚ it's amazing\nthat you remember it so clearly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.3666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈様のファンたるもの、この程度は当然ですわ！\nCMの台詞であれば全て覚えていますし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's only natural for a fan of Mana-sama!\nI remember all of her CM lines…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.2000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "ライブのMCやテレビでのトークに関しても\n印象的な部分をしっかり覚えていますのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And for her live MCs and TV talks‚\nI remember the impressive parts well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.5666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そんなところまで覚えてるのか……\nさすがだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You remember even those parts…\nImpressive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.5000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、今日はお仕事の話が\nあるんでしたわよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of which‚ you said there was some work\nto talk about today‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.4859561883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、そうそう。実はな、すずに……\nお菓子のCMのオファーが来たんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ right‚ right. Actually‚ Suzu…\nyou got an offer for a snack CM.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.5000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "お、お菓子のCM！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A s-snack CM!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.212884188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈様、そしてトリエルと続き……\n私にもついに、出演する番が来たのですわね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana-sama‚ and then TRINITYAiLE…\nIt’s finally my turn to appear in one!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.0333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "確かに放映時期も、ちょうどバレンタインの頃だな\nちなみに、今回はポテトチップスのCMなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The broadcast period is indeed around Valentine's Day.\nBy the way‚ this time it's a potato chip CM.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.1491252408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "はぁぁ……バレンタインのCM……\n麻奈様のように、私も……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haaa… A Valentine's Day CM…\nLike Mana-sama‚ I will…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.2333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "すずは今まで、番組やインタビューでたびたび\nポテトチップスの魅力を語っていただろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu‚ you've often talked about the appeal of\npotato chips on TV and in interviews‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.7333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あの活動が先方の目に留まって\n今回のオファーに繋がったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Those activities caught their attention‚\nand that's what led to this offer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.7666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "はぁぁ～……\n私がバレンタインCMに出演決定……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haaa~…\nI'm going to appear in a Valentine's Day CM…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.9333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "これも、すずの日頃の積み重ねの……\nって……おーい、聞いてるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is also the result of Suzu's usual hard work…\num… Hello? Are you listening?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.6000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "も、もちろん聞いてますわよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-Of course I'm listening!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.4190750445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "CM出演……プレッシャーも伴う大役は\n私にこそふさわしいですわね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Appearing in a CM… is such a big role with pressure‚\nthat means‚ it perfectly suits me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.3666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "今回もばっちりこなして見せますから\n楽しみにしていてくださいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll make sure to do my best this time‚\nso please look forward to it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.6000025432,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9966.66412350001,
          "startTime": 191.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz019.m4a",
      "text": "そうと決まれば、渚に相談して、演技の参考資料を……\nふふふ、楽しみですわ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that it's decided‚ I'll talk to Nagisa and gather references for acting…\nFufufu‚ I'm looking forward to it~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.6000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "やけに浮かれていたな……。まぁ、すずはポテト\nチップスが大好きだしな。それだけ嬉しいってことか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She's awfully excited… Well‚ Suzu loves\npotato chips a lot‚ so I guess that's why she's this happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.2666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
